                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="expression-and-responses-thanking">
                            1. expression and responses thanking</h2><br />
                        Thank.<br />Expression : Thank you so much for your help.<br />Thank you for your attention<br />Thank you very much.<br /><br />Responses :<br />You're welcome!<br />It's okey!<br />Nothing!<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="write-three-expressions-of-thanking-and-the-responses-no-expression-of-thanking-responses-hilmi-2%e2%80%8b">
                            2. Write three expressions of thanking and the responses No Expression of thanking Responses Hilmi 2​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>Write three expressions of thanking and the responses No Expression of thanking Responses Hilmi 2​</p><p></p><p><strong>Thanking expressions:</strong></p><strong>Thanks for your attention.</strong><strong>Thank you very much for your help.</strong><strong>I am grateful for your support.</strong><p><strong>Responses:</strong></p><strong>You are welcome.</strong><strong>Don't mention it.</strong><strong>My pleasure.</strong><p><strong></strong></p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>Jawaban dicetak tebal dan merupakan materi pembelajaran Thanking expressions (mengekspresikan rasa terima kasih) dan Responses (tanggapannya) dalam Bahasa Inggris.</p><p>Tanggapan nomor 1. untuk ekspresi nomor 1. dan seterusnya dan semuanya bisa digunakan secara bergantian / bertukar.</p><p>Ekspresi berterima kasih:
</p>Terima kasih atas perhatianmu.
Terima kasih banyak atas bantuanmu.
Saya berterima kasih atas dukunganmu.
<p>Tanggapan:
</p>Sama sama.
Jangan sebutkan itu.
Dengan senang hati.<p>Semoga membantu ya.</p><br />
