                            8. Answer the questions below!1. Mention five expressions of greeting and its responses!2. Mention five expressions of leave-taking and its responses!3. When do you express your gratitude?4. Mention five expressions of thanking and its responses!5. Mention five expressions of apologizing and its responses!​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p></p><p>1)  -Good morning.</p><p>- Hi. What’s up?</p><p>- Hello. </p><p>- Good afternoon. </p><p>- how are you doing? </p><p></p><p>Response :</p><p></p><p>- Good morning.</p><p>- Nothing much. What’s new with you?</p><p>- Hello. </p><p>- Good afternoon too. </p><p>- I'm fine thank you. </p><p></p><p>2) -Sorry, I have to go now.</p><p>– I’ll talk to you later.</p><p>– It’s been nice talking to you. </p><p>– So, I’ll see you next week</p><p>– I think I’d better be going now.</p><p></p><p></p><p>responses :</p><p></p><p>- Good bye</p><p>‐ Yes of course, it was nice to see you</p><p>‐ So long</p><p>‐ Bye bye</p><p>‐ See you soon</p><p></p><p>3) when i want to thank someone. </p><p></p><p>4) - I’m very grateful for …</p><p>- I’m so grateful for …</p><p>- Thank you very much for …</p><p>- Thank you so much for …</p><p>- Thank you for …</p><p></p><p>Responses :</p><p></p><p>- You’re very/ quite welcome.</p><p>- You’re entirely welcome.</p><p>- Don’t mention it.</p><p>- You’re welcome.</p><p>- It was my pleasure.</p><p></p><p>5) - I’m sorry that… [ex. I was so rude yesterday]</p><p>- It’s my fault.</p><p>(= I am taking responsibility for the problem)</p><p>- Oops, sorry.</p><p>(for very small problems)</p><p>- I should have… [ex. called you and told you I’d be late]</p><p>- (formal) I apologize for… [ex. the delay]</p><p></p><p>Responses :</p><p></p><p>- That’s OK.</p><p>- It happens.</p><p>- No problem.</p><p>- Don’t worry about it.</p><p>- I forgive you.</p><p>(for serious problems)</p><p></p><p>________________________________</p><p>Semoga membantu..^^</p><p>Kalau benar jangan lupa follow dan like✨</p><p>Makasii^^</p><p>|  /   |      |   -—-   |      |   |   |------|</p><p>|/     |      |   | _    | ---- |   |   |       |</p><p>|  \   |___|   __|   |      |   |   |___|</p><br />
