                            18. Mention five expressions of thanking and its  responses</h2><br />
                        1. Thank you so much <br />Response : Your very welcome<br /><br />2. Thank you<br />Response : Your welcome<br /><br />3. Thanks<br />Response : Okay<br /><br />4. Thanks a lot <br />Response : Don't mention it<br /><br />5. You're so kind<br />Response : It don't matter to me<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="thanking123responses123apologizing123responses123%e2%80%8b">
                            19. thanking123responses123apologizing123responses123​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>A. Thanking</p><p>1. Thank you!</p><p>2. Thanks!</p><p>3. Thank you so much! </p><p></p><p>B. Responses </p><p>1. You're welcome!</p><p>2. It's nothing. </p><p>3. Don't mention it! </p><p></p><p>C. Apologizing </p><p>1. I'm sorry. </p><p>2. Pardon me. </p><p>3. I apologize. </p><p></p><p>D. Responses </p><p>1. It's fine. </p><p>2. I forgive you. </p><p>3. Don't do it again. </p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>Ada banyak cara untuk berterima kasih, meminta maaf, begitu pula dengan cara membalasnya, bukan hanya "I'm sorry" atau "Thank you." </p><p></p><p></p><p>Selamat belajar!</p><br />
