                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tuliskan-10-responses-of-thanking-formal-and-informal">
                            24. Tuliskan 10 responses of thanking (formal and informal)</h2><br />
                        1. You're welcome<br />2. No problem<br />3. No worries<br />4. Don't mention it<br />5. My pleasure<br />6. Anytime<br />7. It was a least I could do<br />8. Glad to help<br />9. Sure!<br />10. Thank you (Digunakan jika kamu juga ingin berterimakasih ke orang tersebut).<p>Answer: </p><p>In replying or responding the expression of being grateful or commonly known as 'thank you'.</p><p>Here are the answer: </p><p>(informal) </p><p>- no problem</p><p>- likewise</p><p>- no worries</p><p>- anytime</p><p>- my pleasure</p><p>(formal) </p><p>- Don't mention it. </p><p>- Glad I can help. </p><p>- You're welcome.</p><p>- Don't worry about it.</p><p>- You deserves it. </p><p>Hopefully those are sufficient. </p><p></p><p>Kelas: SMP</p><p>Mapel: English</p><p>Kategori: expression and response  </p><br />
