                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tolong-bantu-ya-make-the-expresions-about-1-greeting-2-taking-leave-3-thanking-4-apologizing-and-the-responses">
                            33. tolong bantu ya.                                                  Make the expresions about: 1. Greeting            2. Taking leave            3. Thanking            4. Apologizing And the responses.​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>1 Greeting</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>maaf kalau salah</p>1. Morning!<br />Morning to.<br />2. I need to go, bye!<br />Bye!<br />3. Thank you so much!<br />No problem my friend.<br />4. Im really sorry...<br />Thats oke.<br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tulis-contoh-thanking-expressions-responses-and-meaning-minimal-15apologize-responses-and-meaning-minimal-15%e2%80%8b">
                            34. Tulis contoh:* Thanking expressions, responses and meaning (minimal 15)*Apologize, responses and meaning (minimal 15)​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>
</p><p>* Ucapan terima kasih, tanggapan dan makna (minimal 15)
</p><p>* Minta maaf, tanggapan dan makna (minimal 15)</p><p><strong>Penjelasan:</strong></p><p>maaf kalau salah</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="practicepractice-minimal-3-expression-and-respond-greeting-thanking-apologizing-and-thanking-%e2%80%8b">
                            35. Practicepractice minimal 3 expression and respond, greeting, thanking, apologizing and thanking.​</h2><br />
                        <p></p><p>Praktek</p><p>berlatih minimal 3 ekspresi dan tanggapi, salam, terima kasih, maaf dan terima kasih.</p><p></p><p>maaf kalo salah </p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="thanking-and-apologizing%e2%80%8b">
                            36. thanking and apologizing​</h2><br />
                        <p>Arti thanking dalam bahasa indonesia adalah berterima kasih</p><p></p><p>Arti apologizing dalam bahasa indonesia adalah meminta maaf</p><p></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="make-a-simple-dialogue8-10-rows-about-apologizing-with-the-responses-or-thanking-with-the-responses%e2%80%8b">
                            37. make a simple dialogue(8-10 rows) about apologizing with the responses or thanking with the responses!​</h2><br />
                        Ara : Hi Ana, where have you been ? <br />Ana : Hi Ara, i’ve just been in the library. What’s wrong ara ? <br />Ara : I just wanna say something<br />Ana : About what ? My pencil ? <br />Ara : Yes. I’m so sorry with you because your pencil has lost from my pencil case. I’m so sorry for at once Ana. <br />Ana : No problem Ara. You can consider it as your gift. Yesterday, you celebrated your birthday, weren’t you ? <br />Ara : Yes. And thanks. <br />Ana : You’re welcome Ara. <br /><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tulis-contoh-thanking-expressions-responses-and-meaning-minimal-15apologize-responses-and-meaning-minimal-15%e2%80%8b">
                            38. Tulis contoh:* Thanking expressions, responses and meaning (minimal 15)*Apologize, responses and meaning (minimal 15)​</h2><br />
                        <p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p>Thanks a lot for make me happy.</p><p></p><p>Thanks very much for help me do this homework.</p><p></p><p>Thank you very much for bring my bag.</p><p></p><p>Thank you so much for believing what I said.</p><p></p><p></p><p>Ally : I will, Mum. I promise. ...</p><p>Andy : I'm sorry, Sir. I'm late to class. ...</p><p>Mr. John: It's okay this time. Please be on time in the future. ...</p><p>Andy : Yes, Sir. I will. ...</p><p>Mira : I apologize. I broke your vase. ...</p><p>Jane: No problem. ...</p><p>Mira : That's very nice of you. ...</p><p>Jane: It's okay, really.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p>Saya tau jawaban saya tidak berguna:'3</p><p>XD</p><p></p><p></p><p>Thanks pointnya:'3</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p>Mangap yak:'D</p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tolong-isiin-dialognya-pleasethanking-apologize-and-responses%e2%80%8b">
                            39. tolong isiin dialognya please,,,,Thanking, apologize and responses​</h2><br />
                        <p>1.I'm Sorry </p><p>2.No Problem</p><p>3.Youre Welcome</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>Lucky  :  i'm sorry Diana. I return your electronic dictionary late.</p><p>Diana  :  no problem. I don't use it yet.</p><p>Lucky  :  thank you for that.</p><p>Diana  :  you're welcome.</p><p></p><p>semoga membantu...</p><p>semangat belajar ^^ </p><p></p><p></p><br />
                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="contoh-kalmat-thanking-expression-dan-responses">
                            40. contoh kalmat thanking (expression dan responses</h2><br />
                        thank you,of course kl gak salah<br />
                    
